metadata.name: Sovereign Souls
metadata.description:
"Sovereign Souls: Embracing Freedom and Authenticity
Religion and sects may provide guidance, but they should not restrict individual freedom. True freedom lies within, as individuals have the power to control their own destiny. To live an authentic life, one must embrace humanity and the principles of truth, compassion, and freedom. Reclaiming one's freedom and embracing self-discovery is the path to a more genuine existence, as every person has the ability to become a Sovereign Soul."
